  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nWhen peers do not support a protocol we penalize them. However we attempt a connection each time we want to send a message out to a peer and penalize them every time.\r\n\r\nWe should add more sophisticated information about a peer, detailing the protocols they support. For protocols that are not required, we should prevent future communications over that protocol. \r\n\r\nThis requires a further discussion about which protocols we will tolerate not being supported. ",
